---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
	title="Events | OAKonsult"
	description="Upcoming events, webinars, and gatherings from OAKonsult Disabilities Outreach."
	path="/events"
>
	<section class="hero">
		<div class="container">
			<p class="section-kicker reveal">Events</p>
			<h1 class="reveal" style="--delay: 0.05s; max-width: 22ch;">Upcoming Events &amp; Webinars</h1>
			<p class="muted-copy reveal" style="--delay: 0.08s;">
				Learn, connect, and contribute to a more inclusive world through OAKonsult events,
				campaign gatherings, and training sessions.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="section-header">
				<p class="section-kicker reveal">Featured Event</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card reveal" style="border-left: 4px solid var(--oak-teal); padding: 2rem;">
				<p style="font-size: var(--text-small); color: var(--oak-teal); font-weight: 600;">FREE WEBINAR</p>
				<h2 style="margin-top: 0.25rem;">From Surviving to Living: A Parent Carer's Roadmap to Healing, Clarity &amp; Strength</h2>
				<p style="margin-top: 0.75rem; color: var(--oak-muted); line-height: 1.8;">
					For many parent carers, life feels like survival &mdash; waking up tired, carrying
					responsibilities that never pause, putting yourself last. This webinar is a safe space
					to begin moving from surviving to living again.
				</p>
				<div style="margin-top: 1rem; display: grid; gap: 0.5rem;">
					<p style="font-weight: 600; color: var(--oak-forest);">Hosted by Mrs Olufunke Adeloye</p>
				</div>
				<ul class="simple-list" style="margin-top: 0.75rem;">
					<li>Why burnout happens (and why it's not your fault)</li>
					<li>How to reconnect with yourself without guilt</li>
					<li>What it means to move from surviving to living</li>
					<li>How healing, clarity, and strength are still possible</li>
				</ul>
				<div class="callout-actions" style="margin-top: 1.25rem;">
					<a class="button button-primary" href="/contact-us">Register Your Interest</a>
					<a class="button button-ghost" href="/blog/from-surviving-to-living">Read More</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section section-alt">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="section-header">
				<p class="section-kicker reveal">More Events</p>
				<h2 class="section-title reveal" style="--delay: 0.05s">Ongoing &amp; Upcoming</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="card-grid">
				<article class="card reveal" style="--delay: 0.08s">
					<p style="font-size: var(--text-small); color: var(--oak-teal); font-weight: 600;">ONGOING</p>
					<h3>Project ME Training (UK)</h3>
					<p>
						An intensive personal-development workshop for parent carers of children and
						young people with disabilities. Based in Bromley with online access.
					</p>
					<a class="inline-link" href="/projectme">Learn more &rarr;</a>
				</article>

				<article class="card reveal" style="--delay: 0.14s">
					<p style="font-size: var(--text-small); color: var(--oak-teal); font-weight: 600;">2025</p>
					<h3>OAK Centre Prime Groundbreaking (Nigeria)</h3>
					<p>
						Groundbreaking for Nigeria's first holistic disability centre in Oolo Town,
						Ogbomoso. Raising funds for Phase 2 construction, staffing, and programme rollout.
					</p>
					<a class="inline-link" href="/oak-centre-prime">Learn more &rarr;</a>
				</article>

				<article class="card reveal" style="--delay: 0.2s">
					<p style="font-size: var(--text-small); color: var(--oak-teal); font-weight: 600;">RECURRING</p>
					<h3>Inclusive Church Training</h3>
					<p>
						Practical training helping churches, schools, and communities welcome and include
						families with disabilities. Available in Nigeria and online.
					</p>
					<a class="inline-link" href="/support-for-churches">Learn more &rarr;</a>
				</article>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="callout reveal" style="text-align: center;">
				<p class="section-kicker">Stay Updated</p>
				<h2>Don't Miss Our Next Event</h2>
				<p style="max-width: 48ch; margin: 0.5rem auto 0;">
					Follow us on Instagram for event announcements, or contact us to be added
					to our mailing list.
				</p>
				<div class="callout-actions" style="justify-content: center;">
					<a class="button button-primary" href="https://www.instagram.com/oakonsult/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
						Follow @oakonsult
					</a>
					<a class="button button-ghost" href="/contact-us">Contact Us</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
